Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.73,0:21:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,业
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.57,0:21:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,每个人打从出生就背负着的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.11,0:22:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.01,0:22:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,西冈好像并没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.41,0:22:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那佐佐木姐的业是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.11,0:22:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你想知道?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.69,0:22:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  失礼了!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.99,0:22:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,太可惜了
